reviewText: Awesome thank you. Fast delivery and perfect product!

What a big year in WSBK. Fairly priced DVD, as some of the other DVDs from other years are two to four times as much money. Worth the money if you want to see some great motorcycle slicing and dicing.

A really complete DVD, featuring all the races in that year's championship, with a nice sound (a lot of v-twin music that year) and also some data about the motorcycles and pilots.
If you are a Troy's fan, this is your video.
